        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="about py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center fw-bold mb-4">About Screening System</h2>
            <p class="text-center mx-auto" style="max-width: 700px;">The Screening System is designed to simplify and expedite the candidate screening process, offering dedicated dashboards and tools for Business Units and Managers to manage, track, and review applications effectively.</p>
